ownerUpdates.text: Spring is the time to treat your lawn right. Fairway’s customized lawn treatments jumpstart healthy growth, prevent weeds, and prepare your lawn for a full season of beauty.
Our lawn treatment services are designed to give your grass the nutrients it needs while controlling weeds and pests that can hold it back. The result? A greener, stronger lawn you’ll love.
Our fertilization services give your lawn exactly what it needs this season—no guesswork, just healthy results.

Did you know? Healthy lawns don’t just happen—they’re built with consistent care, proper nutrients, and seasonal treatments. A well-maintained lawn not only looks great but also helps prevent weeds and pests from taking over.
Lawn Care Tip: Mow high and often! Keeping your grass a bit taller helps shade the soil, retain moisture, and crowd out weeds—promoting a thicker, healthier lawn over time.
Uninvited pests? We’ve got your back. From ants to roaches, spring is a busy time for pests. Fairway’s pest control services help protect your home inside and out.
A healthy lawn starts with the soil. Fairway’s professional treatments support strong root systems and nutrient-rich soil—key to long-lasting, beautiful results.
April is the ideal time to feed your grass, strengthen roots, and get ahead of weeds. Our customized lawn care keeps your lawn green and growing strong.

Lawn Care Tip: Water deeply but less often to encourage strong root growth! Shallow, frequent watering can lead to weak roots and dry patches. Aim for about 1 inch of water per week for a healthier lawn!
Drought Stress? We Can Help! If your lawn isn’t holding moisture well, it may need hydration support. Our treatments improve soil moisture retention for a healthier, greener lawn!
